					<img itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject" alt="A Franchisee Gym Pumps up Profits by Going Green" src="https://assets.entrepreneur.com/content/16x9/822/russ-golan-retro-fitness.jpg" rel="share" />

					
							
								
